{"type": "article", "id": 16232, "title": "COFFEE TALK", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-19T06:00:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061512060fZ2YShu1Cbk4GOz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个颇具实验性质的设计，8 个马克杯割断把手，只在杯身上印了几行关于设计的定义和讨论的标语，白底黑字，颇有对话的意味。设计者想要引起人们对设计本身的辩证思考，这些消失的把手保留了粗糙断面，却并不影响杯子的使用，反而令人思考那些先入为主的设计。<a href=\"http://fdnstudiolab.com/chapter1thepark/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143557pdjWZPGSszbI8oQh.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"701\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143557lHO5FPx7RJ2mzgTG.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"701\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143558WSUG6pbQHtfAL0O1.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"701\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261435583vTXHaf24hJ0sdek.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"701\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143559DdmRbalANpyqhUFu.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"701\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}